pyhp (1.3-1) stable; urgency=low

  * fourth release
  * add max_size and ttl caching options
  * add config parameter for cache handlers
  * add .is_available for cache handlers
  * fix header_remove
  * fix header_register_callback
  * add more customizable Request handling
  * add --config argument
  * rework register_shutdown_function to use atexit

